nejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-sun size-4 scale-100 rotate-0 transition-all dark:scale-0 dark:-rotate-90\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"4\"></circle><path d=\"M12 2v2\"></path><path d=\"M12 20v2\"></path><path d=\"m4.93 4.93 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m17.66 17.66 1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"M2 12h2\"></path><path d=\"M20 12h2\"></path><path d=\"m6.34 17.66-1.41 1.41\"></path><path d=\"m19.07 4.93-1.41 1.41\"></path></svg><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon absolute size-4 scale-0 rotate-90 transition-all dark:scale-100 dark:rotate-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></button></div></div></nav><div class=\"flex flex-1 flex-col\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl flex-1 px-4 py-6 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><div class=\"flex gap-6\"><main class=\"min-w-0 flex-1\"><div class=\"mb-4 hidden justify-center lg:flex\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"leaderboard\"></div></div><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"SoftwareApplication\",\"name\":\"Free Invoice Generator\",\"description\":\"Create professional invoices with custom templates, tax calculations, and instant PDF export.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/invoice-generator\",\"applicationCategory\":\"UtilitiesApplication\",\"operatingSystem\":\"Web\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"}}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"HowTo\",\"name\":\"How to Create a Professional Invoice\",\"description\":\"Create a print-ready PDF invoice with line items, tax, and template customization, then download or save it locally.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/tools/invoice-generator\",\"step\":[{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Enter your business details\",\"text\":\"Add your company name, address, email, and optionally upload your logo.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Add your client information\",\"text\":\"Fill in the client name, email, and billing address.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":3,\"name\":\"Add line items\",\"text\":\"Enter each product or service with a description, quantity, unit type, and unit price. Enable per-item taxes if needed.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":4,\"name\":\"Choose a template and customize\",\"text\":\"Pick from Modern, Classic, or Compact templates. Set your brand accent color, date format, and invoice status.\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"position\":5,\"name\":\"Download or save your invoice\",\"text\":\"Download a print-ready PDF, save to your invoice history for later, or export as JSON for backup.\"}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is this invoice generator really free?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need to create an account?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No. You can start creating invoices immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Is my data private and secure?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Your invoice data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your business information stays completely private.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What invoice templates are available?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Three professional templates are included: Modern (clean and minimal), Classic (traditional business style), and Compact (dense layout for invoices with many line items).\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I add my company logo?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Upload your company logo in PNG, JPEG, or SVG format and it will appear on your invoice and PDF export.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What currencies are supported?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"20 major currencies are supported including USD, EUR, GBP, CAD, AUD, JPY, CHF, INR, and more. Currency symbols and decimal formatting are handled automatically.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I save my invoices?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Your current draft auto-saves as you type. You can also save invoices to your history for later access, duplicate them, or export all invoices as JSON for backup.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I track invoice status?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes. Mark each invoice as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue. The status appears as a watermark on the PDF and in your invoice history.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do I print my invoice?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Click the Print button to open your browser's print dialog, or download the PDF and print from your PDF viewer. Both options produce professional, print-ready output.\"}}]}</script><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"BreadcrumbList\",\"itemListElement\":[{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":1,\"name\":\"Home\",\"item\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/\"},{\"@type\":\"ListItem\",\"position\":2,\"name\":\"Invoice Generator\"}]}</script><nav aria-label=\"Breadcrumb\" class=\"mb-4\"><ol class=\"flex items-center gap-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a></li><li class=\"flex items-center gap-1\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-right size-3.5 shrink-0\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m9 18 6-6-6-6\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-foreground\">Invoice Generator</span></li></ol></nav><h1 class=\"text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight\">Free Invoice Generator</h1><p class=\"mt-2 text-lg text-muted-foreground\">Create professional invoices with custom templates, automatic tax calculations, and instant PDF download — a free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave. No sign-up required.</p><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"Person\",\"name\":\"James Nicolaus\",\"jobTitle\":\"Builder & Maintainer, Free Tool Shed\",\"description\":\"James Nicolaus builds and maintains every tool on Free Tool Shed. Each tool is designed, tested in real browsers across desktop and mobile, and shipped only after handling the messy edge cases — large files, slow connections, unusual inputs — that paid alternatives often hide behind sign-up walls.\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com/about\",\"worksFor\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Free Tool Shed\",\"url\":\"https://freetoolshed.com\"}}</script><p class=\"mt-3 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">Built and maintained by<!-- --> <a class=\"font-medium text-foreground underline-offset-4 hover:underline\" rel=\"author\" href=\"/about\">James Nicolaus</a></p><section aria-label=\"Summary\" class=\"mt-6 rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-4\"><p class=\"text-sm leading-relaxed text-foreground\">Free Tool Shed&#x27;s Invoice Generator creates print-ready PDF invoices entirely in your browser — no sign-up, no email, no upload. Pick from three templates (Modern, Classic, Compact), add your logo, calculate per-item taxes across 20 currencies, and track invoices as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue. Drafts auto-save locally. A free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave.</p></section><div class=\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">3 Professional Templates</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Choose from Modern, Classic, or Compact layouts. Each template is fully customizable with your brand colors and company logo.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Instant PDF Export</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Download print-ready PDF invoices in one click. Your data never leaves your browser — everything is processed locally on your device.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">20 Currencies Supported</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Invoice clients worldwide with automatic currency formatting for USD, EUR, GBP, JPY, CAD, AUD, INR, and 13 more.</p></div><div class=\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><h2 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Invoice History &amp; Status Tracking</h2><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Save invoices to your local history, track them as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue, and export/import JSON backups. Auto-save keeps your current draft safe.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><!--$!--><template data-dgst=\"BAILOUT_TO_CLIENT_SIDE_RENDERING\"></template><!--/$--></div><div class=\"my-8 flex justify-center\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:728px;height:90px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"mid-content\"></div></div><div class=\"mt-16 space-y-12\"><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"separator\" aria-orientation=\"horizontal\" data-slot=\"separator\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border data-horizontal:h-px data-horizontal:w-full data-vertical:w-px data-vertical:self-stretch\"></div><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Free Invoice Generator Online</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Create polished, professional invoices in minutes — completely free and without signing up. Free Tool Shed&#x27;s invoice generator is a free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave. Your data never leaves your browser, so your business information stays private. Just fill in your details, pick a template, and download a print-ready PDF.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Features</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">3 professional PDF templates (Modern, Classic, Compact)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Invoice history — save, load, duplicate, and manage invoices</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Status tracking — mark invoices as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Export and import invoices as JSON for backup and migration</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Automatic tax calculations with per-item tax rates</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">20 currencies with proper symbol and decimal formatting</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Company logo upload — appears on invoice and PDF</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Flexible payment terms (Net 15, 30, 60 or custom)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Unit types for line items (hour, day, item, unit, service)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">4 date format options (Month D YYYY, MM/DD, DD/MM, YYYY-MM-DD)</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Payment link field — include a payment URL on your invoice</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Save company defaults for faster invoice creation</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Percentage or flat-rate discounts</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Auto-incrementing invoice numbers</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Live preview with real-time updates as you type</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><span class=\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"></span><span class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Custom accent color to match your brand</span></li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">How to Create a Professional Invoice</h2><ol class=\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-4\"><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-sm font-semibold text-brand\">1</span><div><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Enter your business details</h3><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Add your company name, address, email, and optionally upload your logo.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-sm font-semibold text-brand\">2</span><div><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Add your client information</h3><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Fill in the client name, email, and billing address.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-sm font-semibold text-brand\">3</span><div><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Add line items</h3><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Enter each product or service with a description, quantity, unit type, and unit price. Enable per-item taxes if needed.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-sm font-semibold text-brand\">4</span><div><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Choose a template and customize</h3><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Pick from Modern, Classic, or Compact templates. Set your brand accent color, date format, and invoice status.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-4\"><span class=\"flex h-7 w-7 shrink-0 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-brand/10 text-sm font-semibold text-brand\">5</span><div><h3 class=\"font-medium\">Download or save your invoice</h3><p class=\"mt-0.5 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Download a print-ready PDF, save to your invoice history for later, or export as JSON for backup.</p></div></li></ol></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-tips\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-tips\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Tips from Building <!-- -->the Invoice Generator</h2><p class=\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\">Notes from designing and testing this tool — what we kept in mind, the edge cases we worked around, and the small choices that make the difference between a tool that ships and one that breaks on real input.</p><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Lock the currency before sending the invoice</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Currency formatting changes decimal separator and symbol placement. Pick the currency first so your line items don&#x27;t need to be re-entered when you switch from USD to EUR or JPY.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Per-item tax rates beat a global rate</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Real-world invoices mix taxable and non-taxable items — services in some jurisdictions, software in others. We built per-item tax so you don&#x27;t have to split a single job into multiple invoices.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Status watermarks are deliberate</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Draft/Sent/Paid/Overdue status doesn&#x27;t just live in the history list — it watermarks the PDF so a stale draft can&#x27;t be mistaken for a billed invoice.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M15 14c.2-1 .7-1.7 1.5-2.5 1-.9 1.5-2.2 1.5-3.5A6 6 0 0 0 6 8c0 1 .2 2.2 1.5 3.5.7.7 1.3 1.5 1.5 2.5\"></path><path d=\"M9 18h6\"></path><path d=\"M10 22h4\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Export JSON before clearing browser data</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Invoice history lives in localStorage, which gets wiped by &quot;Clear browsing data.&quot; The JSON export is your portable backup; import it anywhere or restore after a browser reset.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-mistakes\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-mistakes\" class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2><ul class=\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3\"><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Forgetting payment terms</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">An invoice without explicit terms (Net 15, Net 30, etc.) defaults to vague expectations. Pick a term so the client knows when payment is due and you can mark it Overdue accurately.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Using the wrong date format for the client&#x27;s country</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">MM/DD vs DD/MM regularly causes disputes when a US-formatted date is read in Europe. Set the date format that matches your client&#x27;s region, not yours.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Skipping the logo upload &quot;for now&quot;</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">An invoice without a logo reads as a template printout, not a billing document. Upload it once, save it as a company default, and every future invoice picks it up.</p></div></li><li class=\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-triangle-alert mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-pink-500\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m21.73 18-8-14a2 2 0 0 0-3.48 0l-8 14A2 2 0 0 0 4 21h16a2 2 0 0 0 1.73-3\"></path><path d=\"M12 9v4\"></path><path d=\"M12 17h.01\"></path></svg><div><h3 class=\"text-sm font-semibold\">Not saving a copy before printing</h3><p class=\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Printing doesn&#x27;t save the invoice to your history. Save to history (or export the PDF) first — then print.</p></div></li></ul></section><section aria-labelledby=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"rounded-lg border border-brand/30 bg-brand/5 p-5\"><h2 id=\"tool-insights-takeaways\" class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight\">Key Takeaways</h2><ul class=\"mt-3 space-y-2\"><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Free Tool Shed&#x27;s Invoice Generator creates print-ready PDF invoices entirely client-side; no upload, no sign-up.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Three templates, 20 currencies, per-item tax, status tracking, and JSON export/import are all included.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">Drafts auto-save locally; the JSON export is the portable backup if you clear browser data.</span></li><li class=\"flex items-start gap-2\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check mt-0.5 size-4 shrink-0 text-brand\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-sm text-foreground\">It is a free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave for one-off and small-volume invoicing.</span></li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Free FreshBooks Alternative</h2><div class=\"mt-4 overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full max-w-3xl text-sm\"><thead><tr class=\"border-b border-border text-left\"><th class=\"py-3 pr-4 font-medium\">Feature</th><th class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium text-brand\">Free Tool Shed</th><th class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">FreshBooks</th><th class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">QuickBooks</th><th class=\"px-4 py-3 font-medium\">Wave</th></tr></thead><tbody class=\"divide-y divide-border\"><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Price</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Free</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">From $19/mo</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">From $30/mo</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Free*</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Sign-up Required</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">PDF Export</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Custom Templates</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">3 included</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Limited</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Logo Upload</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Multi-Currency</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">20 currencies</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Limited</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Invoice History</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes (local)</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Status Tracking</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Limited</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Export/Import JSON</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Client-Side Privacy</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">No</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Tax Calculations</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Recurring Invoices</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr><tr><td class=\"py-2.5 pr-4 font-medium\">Payment Processing</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-brand\">No</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td><td class=\"px-4 py-2.5 text-muted-foreground\">Yes</td></tr></tbody></table><p class=\"mt-2 text-xs text-muted-foreground\">* Wave is free for invoicing but requires account creation and stores your data on their servers.</p></div></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Frequently Asked Questions</h2><div class=\"mt-4 max-w-3xl space-y-2\"><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Is this invoice generator really free?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes, completely free. No hidden fees, no premium tiers, and no sign-up required. The tool is ad-supported so it can remain free for everyone.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Do I need to create an account?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">No. You can start creating invoices immediately without signing up or providing any personal information.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Is my data private and secure?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Your invoice data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your business information stays completely private.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">What invoice templates are available?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Three professional templates are included: Modern (clean and minimal), Classic (traditional business style), and Compact (dense layout for invoices with many line items).</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Can I add my company logo?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Upload your company logo in PNG, JPEG, or SVG format and it will appear on your invoice and PDF export.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">What currencies are supported?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">20 major currencies are supported including USD, EUR, GBP, CAD, AUD, JPY, CHF, INR, and more. Currency symbols and decimal formatting are handled automatically.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Can I save my invoices?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Your current draft auto-saves as you type. You can also save invoices to your history for later access, duplicate them, or export all invoices as JSON for backup.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">Can I track invoice status?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Yes. Mark each invoice as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue. The status appears as a watermark on the PDF and in your invoice history.</p></details><details class=\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\"><summary class=\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\">How do I print my invoice?</summary><p class=\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\">Click the Print button to open your browser&#x27;s print dialog, or download the PDF and print from your PDF viewer. Both options produce professional, print-ready output.</p></details></div></section></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><aside class=\"hidden w-[300px] shrink-0 lg:block\"><div class=\"sticky top-20\"><div class=\"flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded \" style=\"width:300px;height:250px;max-width:100%\" data-ad-slot=\"sidebar\"></div><div id=\"tool-guide-portal\"></div></div></aside></div></div></div><footer class=\"border-t border-border bg-muted/40\"><div class=\"mx-auto flex max-w-7xl flex-col items-center gap-4 px-4 py-8 sm:flex-row sm:justify-between sm:px-6 lg:px-8\"><p class=\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> Free Tool Shed. All rights reserved.</p><nav class=\"flex gap-4 text-sm text-muted-foreground\"><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/contact\">Contact</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/privacy\">Privacy</a><a class=\"transition-colors hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/terms\">Terms</a></nav></div></footer><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0eyplc079uusk.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[83661,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0ag6f0zogt0qg.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04p0ygcx_g620.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0_pa1c_tsbiw0.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/10nuyoal1pib2.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[46798,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zif8_3mgcc0x.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0zv.me6xdrdsz.js\\