ded: Modern (clean and minimal), Classic (traditional business style), and Compact (dense layout for invoices with many line items).\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I add my company logo?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"Can I add my company logo?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Upload your company logo in PNG, JPEG, or SVG format and it will appear on your invoice and PDF export.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What currencies are supported?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"What currencies are supported?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"20 major currencies are supported including USD, EUR, GBP, CAD, AUD, JPY, CHF, INR, and more. Currency symbols and decimal formatting are handled automatically.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I save my invoices?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"Can I save my invoices?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Your current draft auto-saves as you type. You can also save invoices to your history for later access, duplicate them, or export all invoices as JSON for backup.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I track invoice status?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"Can I track invoice status?\"}],\"$L48\"]}],\"$L49\"]}]]}]\n39:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h