ser — no sign-up, no email, no upload. Pick from three templates (Modern, Classic, Compact), add your logo, calculate per-item taxes across 20 currencies, and track invoices as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue. Drafts auto-save locally. A free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave.\"}]}]\n9:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"3 Professional Templates\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Choose from Modern, Classic, or Compact layouts. Each template is fully customizable with your brand colors and company logo.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Instant PDF Export\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Download print-ready PDF invoices in one click. Your data never leaves your browser — everything is processed locally on your device.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"20 Currencies Supported\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Invoice clients worldwide with automatic currency formatting for USD, EUR, GBP, JPY, CAD, AUD, INR, and 13 more.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Invoice History & Status Tracking\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Save invoices to your local history, track them as Draft, Sent, Paid, or Overdue, and export/import JSON backups. Auto-save keeps your current draft safe.\"}]]}]]}]\na:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-8\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L11\",null,{}]}]\nb:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"my-8 flex justify-center\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L12\",null,{\"slot\":\"mid-content\"}]}]\nc:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-16 space-y-12\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L13\",null,{}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Free Invoice Generator Online\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-3 max-w-3xl text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Create polished, professional invoices in minutes — completely free and without signing up. Free Tool Shed's invoice generator is a free alternative to FreshBooks, QuickBooks, and Wave. Your data never leaves your browser, so your business information stays private. Just fill in your details, pick a template, and download a print-ready PDF.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"section\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight\",\"children\":\"Features\"}],[\"$\",\"ul\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-4 grid max-w-3xl gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"li\",\"3 professional PDF templates (Modern, Classic, Compact)\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"3 professional PDF templates (Modern, Classic, Compact)\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Invoice history — save, load, duplicate, and manage invoices\",{\"className\":\"flex items-start gap-2\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1.5 h-1.5 w-1.5 shrink-0 rounded-full bg-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"span\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Invoice history — save, load, duplicate, and manage invoices\"}]]}]