rrency first so your line items don't need to be re-entered when you switch from USD to EUR or JPY.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Per-item tax rates beat a global rate\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$1c:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Per-item tax rates beat a global rate\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Real-world invoices mix taxable and non-taxable items — services in some jurisdictions, software in others. We built per-item tax so you don't have to split a single job into multiple invoices.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Status watermarks are deliberate\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$1c:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-sm font-semibold\",\"children\":\"Status watermarks are deliberate\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Draft/Sent/Paid/Overdue status doesn't just live in the history list — it watermarks the PDF so a stale draft can't be mistaken for a billed invoice.\"}]]}]]}],[\"$\",\"li\",\"Export JSON before clearing browser data\",{\"className\":\"flex gap-3 rounded-lg border border-border bg-card p-4\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"$L10\",null,{\"iconNode\":\"$1c:0:props:children:2:props:children:0:props:children:0:props:iconNode\",\"className\":\"lucide-lightbulb mt-0.5 size-5 shrink-0 text-brand\"}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"children\":[[\"$\",\"h3\",null,{\"className\":\"text-s