 and secure?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Your invoice data never leaves your browser. All processing happens client-side on your device, so your business information stays completely private.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What invoice templates are available?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"What invoice templates are available?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Three professional templates are included: Modern (clean and minimal), Classic (traditional business style), and Compact (dense layout for invoices with many line items).\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I add my company logo?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"Can I add my company logo?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"Yes. Upload your company logo in PNG, JPEG, or SVG format and it will appear on your invoice and PDF export.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"What currencies are supported?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-medium marker:text-brand\",\"children\":\"What currencies are supported?\"}],[\"$\",\"p\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-2 text-sm text-muted-foreground\",\"children\":\"20 major currencies are supported including USD, EUR, GBP, CAD, AUD, JPY, CHF, INR, and more. Currency symbols and decimal formatting are handled automatically.\"}]]}],[\"$\",\"details\",\"Can I save my invoices?\",{\"className\":\"group rounded-lg border border-border px-4 py-3\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"summary\",null,{\"className\":\"cursor-pointer font-m